{"pagetitle": [" SSARIS Advisors LLC"], "text": ["ABSOLUTE RETURN INVESTMENT STRATEGIES ADVISORY SERVICES SUMMARY SSARIS advises institutional investors on all matters related to hedge fund and fund of hedge funds investing Our mission is to provide a \u00e2\u0080\u009cbest practices\u00e2\u0080\u009d approach to the construction and ongoing monitoring of hedge fund related portfolios SSARIS believes a prudent risk management program must consider the qualitative risks intrinsic to investment management Among these are the program structure the interpretation of quantitative data and appropriate manager selection based on pre-determined risk and return objectives SSARIS believes this is particularly important in the realm of hedge fund investing where information availability is not standardized Key services may include qualitative performance monitoring performance analysis peer group analysis manager due diligence and non-discretionary manager recommendation \u00a0 SSARIS Advisors LLC \u00a9 2012 SSARIS ADVISORS LLC All rights reserved VER 12Env:PROD"], "pageurl": ["http://wwwssariscom/UI/Advisory/adsummaryaspx"], "siteurl": ["ssariscom"]}
