{"pagetitle": ["Charterhouse Equity Partners LLC - Executive Partnerships"], "text": ["Executive Partnerships The following examples provide overviews of how Charterhouse partners with executives: \"We have now worked with Charterhouse for over thirty years and we consider Tom and his team to be part of our professional family By sharing our visions and combining the skills of our teams we have developed a formula for long-term success I have a tremendous amount of respect for the team\" \"Charterhouses business model embraces entrepreneurs and entrepreneurial visions I approached the firm with an idea they worked with me to develop it into an actionable transaction and we were very successful at building a leading company I have subsequently been involved in numerous Charterhouse companies - a testament to the firms strong ability to retain managers and build great relationships\" \"I have approached Charterhouse twice seeking growth capital for my businesses In each case Charterhouse has provided the strategic and financial support to enable the companies to take advantage of the explosive growth in the wireless communications industry After a successful partnership in building a wireless cell tower company I had no hesitation approaching the Charterhouse team again to partner in building a distributed antenna systems company In an environment like the present it is increasingly important to know how your partners think and act Charterhouse has proven to be a trusted and value-added partner \"When I was selling my business Charterhouse was among a group of financial sponsors interested in acquiring the company In the process Charterhouse differentiated itself from the other buyers; exhibiting deep knowledge of the industry and bringing a well-thought-out strategy of how to continue to build my business As we now look to build an integrated facilities services company together I know that I have partnered with a team that can provide value-added strategic and financial support and bring years of experience to the process? The Information on these pages is intended solely for the benefit of persons who might be aware of investment opportunities that would interest Charterhouse Charterhouses services are provided only to a limited number of private investment funds; Charterhouse does not make its services available to the public 2012 CHARTERHOUSE EQUITY PARTNERS LLC"], "pageurl": ["http://wwwcharterhouseequitycom/ExecutivePartnershipshtml"], "siteurl": ["charterhouseequitycom"]}
