{"pagetitle": ["Gerald Parsky Aurora Resurgence"], "text": ["Team Chairman Managing Partner Partner Partner Partner and GC Principal Vice President Vice President Associate Associate Associate Analyst CFO Controller Advisory Board Advisory Board Advisory Board Advisory Board Executive Advisor Executive Advisor Gerald Parsky Chairman Gerald Parsky is the Chairman of Aurora Capital Group and a member of the Investment CommitteeMr Parsky founded Aurora Capital Group in 1991 Previously Mr Parsky served as Assistant Secretary of the Treasury for International Affairs from 1974 to 1977 For the next 14 years Mr Parsky was affiliated with the law firm of Gibson Dunn & Crutcher where he was a Senior Partner and member of the Executive and Management CommitteesMr Parsky received a JD from the University of Virginia Law School and a Bachelor of Arts in English from Princeton University \u00a9 2015"], "pageurl": ["http://wwwaurorarescom/team/gerald-parsky/"], "siteurl": ["aurorarescom"]}
